          "prompt_html": "<h1>MULTIPLE CHOICE 11</h1><p><strong>Questions 11 - 15</strong></p><p>Choose the correct letter, <strong>A, B or C</strong>.</p><p><strong>Solaris Hotel and Holiday Village - Food Options</strong></p><p>11 Which restaurant serves three meals every day?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    The Harvest restaurant</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    The Dene restaurant</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    The Mekong restaurant</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>12 Where is it possible to choose dishes other than those that appear on the menu?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    In none of the restaurants</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    In the Mekong and Dene restaurants</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    In all three restaurants</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>13 Which restaurant's menu is based on a specific food group?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    The Harvest restaurant's</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    The Dene restaurant's</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    The Mekong restaurant's</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>14 Which option do you NOT have to pay extra for?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    Menu items</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    Specials</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    Alcoholic drinks</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>15 What additional facility does the hotel offer?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    An all-night bar</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    A late-night food service</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    A nightclub</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>",
